01:09:34,800 --> 01:09:38,320
But Melville does, in a funny way, worry about it.

746
01:09:38,321 --> 01:09:45,200
He worries about what if they fish out, what if they get rid of all the sperm whales, which are the source of the unrepresentable?

747
01:09:45,201 --> 01:09:46,561
Where will we be then?

748
01:09:47,201 --> 01:09:49,200
And his answer is they can't do it.

